  'focusScopeDesc' => 
  array (
    'en_US' => '<p><em>Journal of Numerical Analysis and Approximation Theory</em> is a peer reviewed journal published under the auspices of the <a href="http://academiaromana.ro">Romanian Academy</a>. </p><p>The journal publishes original papers in the areas of <strong>Numerical Analysis</strong> and <strong>Approximation Theory</strong>. </p><p>The Editors put strong emphasis on originality and applicability of the results.</p><p>The journal is reviewed by <a href="http://www.ams.org/mathscinet/">Mathematical Reviews</a> and <a href="http://www.zbmath.org/">Zentralblatt für Mathematik</a>. </p><p>In addition to presenting research papers, our journal publishes survey articles and book reviews. The preferably language is English; only in well-argued and exceptional situations, the journal may accept papers written in French or German, in which case the paper must contain an English translation of the title, abstract and keywords (ICTP will make efforts to provide an English translation of the whole paper).</p><p>The journal is addressed to all applied mathematicians and other specialists interested in modern developments of Numerical Analysis and Approximation Theory, and in their using in research, teaching and technology. </p><p>At present, the journal has numerous subscriptions and exchanges with reputed journals all over the world. </p>',
